episodes.title: Police Arrest 19 Suspects In Connection With Owo Cult Clash
Police K!ll Wanted Cult Leader, 2-Baba After 6-Month Manhunt
episodes.description:
Police in Rivers State have displayed the corpse of a cult groupleader who was declared wanted for the murder of  Divisional PoliceOfficer, Bako Angbashim.

This comes few days after it was reported that the suspect had beenkilled in a shootout with the police.
